{"sections":{"main":{"type":"article-template","custom_css":[".article .section-header__title {text-transform: none;}"],"settings":{"image_hero":false,"blog_show_tags":true,"blog_show_date":false,"blog_show_comments":false,"blog_show_author":false,"social_sharing_blog":false}},"background_image_text_GXGKcF":{"type":"background-image-text","settings":{"classes":"custom-banner-img","subtitle":"","title":"","text":"","text_color":"#000000","button_label":"","button_link":"","bg_color":"#000000","btn_color":"#ffffff","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGBR0149-01BVPN_7_1.jpg","layout":"left","height":550,"framed":false,"parallax":true,"parallax_direction":"top","lazyload_images":true}},"rich_text_X4YKkz":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_reYjpA":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p>Black diamonds are a bold statement in men's fashion, bringing both elegance and an edge to your style. Whether it’s a casual outing or a formal occasion, MARCO DAL MASO’s black diamond jewelry allows you to stand out without overdoing it.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_reYjpA"],"settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":true,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"text_and_image_ebhjYT":{"type":"text-and-image","settings":{"custom_id":"","full_width":false,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGAN0047-01BVEN_1__G.webp","image_mask":"none","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","caption":"","title":"","text":"<h3><strong>Casual Confidence: Elevate Your Everyday Look<\/strong><\/h3><p><\/p><p>Black diamonds aren’t just for special occasions—they can easily be integrated into your daily outfits. A simple black diamond ring or a refined bracelet adds a subtle yet stylish touch to even the most casual attire.<\/p><p><\/p><p>For a laid-back look, try pairing Ulysses’s black diamond and black enamel ring with jeans and a leather jacket. The understated shine of the diamonds contrasts perfectly with rugged materials, giving you a polished yet relaxed vibe.<\/p>","html":"","button_label":"","button_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/ulysses-slick-ring-oxidized-silver-black-diamond-black-enamel-agan0047-01bven","button_labels":"","button_links":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"50","layout":"right","body_bg":"#ffffff","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"text_and_image_JfTUUA":{"type":"text-and-image","settings":{"custom_id":"","full_width":false,"image_mask":"none","image2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGCL123-01BLSBEN.jpg","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","caption":"","title":"","text":"<p>A black diamond necklace like Acies Triple Black Cocoon <\/p><p>Necklace works well with a basic t-shirt, especially in monochrome tones like black or white.<\/p><p><\/p><p>This combination keeps things simple while allowing the jewelry to stand out. Layer with other chains for a more dynamic effect.<\/p>","html":"","button_label":"","button_link":"\/products\/ulysses-slick-oxidized-ring-with-black-diamond-black-enamel?_pos=4&_sid=82799d952&_ss=r","button_labels":"","button_links":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"50","layout":"left","body_bg":"#ffffff","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"rich_text_cAqpJe":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_xM6FrM":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<h3><strong>Making a Statement at Formal Events with MARCO DAL MASO Diamonds<\/strong><\/h3><p><\/p><p>Formal occasions offer the perfect opportunity to bring out your boldest black diamond pieces by MARCO DAL MASO. Whether you're attending a wedding, gala, or business event, black diamonds add a touch of luxury and intrigue to your outfit.<\/p><p><\/p><p>Our black diamond rings can be the centerpiece of your look, complementing a sleek black suit or tuxedo. The deep tone of the diamonds pairs especially well with darker clothing, creating a unified, sophisticated aesthetic.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_xM6FrM"],"settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"left","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"text_columns_MdreXB":{"type":"text-columns","blocks":{"text_block_FQkTEP":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGAN0061-01BV_7d10ff4e-6783-4615-a438-e8a33b5de896.jpg","image_mask":"none","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"","style_link":false,"chat_btn":false,"button_label":"","button_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/moneta-pave-signet-ring-oxidized-silver-with-black-diamonds-and-tsavorite-agan0055-06bv"}},"text_block_TrdrQP":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"enable_image":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGAN0061-01BV_1_1__G.webp","image_mask":"none","image_width":650,"title":"","text":"","style_link":false,"chat_btn":false,"button_label":"","button_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/gladiator-signet-ring-with-black-diamonds-agan0061-02bv"}}},"block_order":["text_block_FQkTEP","text_block_TrdrQP"],"settings":{"title":"","btntext":"","btnurl":"","text":"","align_text":"center","divider":false,"mobile_link":""}},"text_and_image_ktDTVz":{"type":"text-and-image","settings":{"custom_id":"","full_width":false,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AGCL122-02BVW.jpg","image_mask":"none","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"","caption":"","title":"","text":"<p>For a formal setting, wearing a MARCO DAL MASO black diamond necklace with a minimalist design can add just the right amount of elegance without overwhelming your look.<br\/><br\/>Keep the rest of your accessories subtle to let the diamonds take center stage.<br\/><br\/>Check out Moneta Black Diamond Pendant.<\/p>","html":"","button_label":"","button_link":"\/products\/ulysses-slick-oxidized-ring-with-black-diamond-black-enamel?_pos=4&_sid=82799d952&_ss=r","button_labels":"","button_links":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"50","layout":"right","body_bg":"#ffffff","divider":false,"top_paddi